S-BH, rather than NS-NS, mergers.\nOur model implies a NS-BH merger detection rate by LIGO which, in steady-state,\nis comparable to or greater than that of NS-NS mergers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2018 19:00:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Dec 2018 18:32:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-20"}
