 observing band under consideration. This procedure\nmay be carried out for each location around a telescope site, in order to\nobtain a map of potentially problematic wind turbine positions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2018 22:33:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-13"}
