o a procedure, based on the concept of loss function, to obtain a\nfinal classification fulfilling some requirements given by the decision maker\nand taking into account the hierarchy of criteria and the probabilistic\nassignments obtained applying SMAA. Also this procedure can be applied to any\nclassification Electre method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Dec 2018 12:50:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2019 11:04:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-30"}
